"The little brother

64
00:05:23,740 --> 00:05:26,743
killed his big brother."

65
00:05:27,535 --> 00:05:29,495
[ominous music sting]

66
00:05:29,579 --> 00:05:35,418
[unsettling music continues]

67
00:05:48,264 --> 00:05:49,932
[foreboding music sting]

68
00:05:52,810 --> 00:05:58,983
[foreboding music continues]

69
00:06:09,327 --> 00:06:15,541
[foreboding music continues]

70
00:06:23,633 --> 00:06:29,472
[breathing in awe]

71
