219
00:16:50,217 --> 00:16:55,973
[sorrowful music playing]

220
00:17:02,187 --> 00:17:03,731
[Tessie] <i>Luis.</i>

221
00:17:07,651 --> 00:17:09,445
<i>I'm so tired.</i>

222
00:17:09,528 --> 00:17:14,450
[sorrowful music continues]

223
00:17:15,784 --> 00:17:17,786
<i>Why did you have to go?</i>

224
00:17:18,579 --> 00:17:20,998
[sniffles, sobs]

225
00:17:22,332 --> 00:17:25,919
<i>Why did you leave us so early?</i>

226
00:17:26,003 --> 00:17:31,341
- [sorrowful music continues]
- [sobbing]

227
00:17:31,425 --> 00:17:34,595
<i>Luis, your sons need you.</i>

228
00:17:34,678 --> 00:17:36,889
<i>They really do.</i>

229
00:17:37,639 --> 00:17:40,309
[sniffles, sobbing]

230
00:17:41,477 --> 00:17:42,603
[sniffles]

231
00:17:45,189 --> 00:17:46,523
[grunts softly]

232
00:17:46,607 --> 00:17:52,237
[sorrowful music continues]

233
00:17:52,321 --> 00:17:55,282
[Tessie] <i>They're so naughty. </i>[chuckling]

234
00:17:56,283 --> 00:17:58,118
[Tessie whimpers]

235
00:17:58,202 --> 00:18:02,039
[sniffling, sobbing]

236
00:18:03,999 --> 00:18:05,626
[sniffling]

237
00:18:05,709 --> 00:18:07,920
[sobbing continues]

238
00:18:10,339 --> 00:18:11,465
<i>Ma?</i>

239
00:18:12,007 --> 00:18:14,009
[Tessie sobs, gulps]

240
00:18:14,885 --> 00:18:16,512
<i>Patrick.</i>

241
00:18:16,595 --> 00:18:18,013
<i>Patrick.</i> [sniffles]

242
00:18:18,097 --> 00:18:19,932
<i>Patrick, my son, come here.</i>

243
00:18:20,557 --> 00:18:21,517
<i>Come here.</i>

244
00:18:22,101 --> 00:18:24,311
<i>Aw, Patrick.</i>

245
00:18:25,145 --> 00:18:27,773
<i>My sweet son.</i>

246
00:18:28,816 --> 00:18:29,900
[chuckling]

247
00:18:29,983 --> 00:18:32,402
[breathes deeply]

248
00:18:33,195 --> 00:18:35,531
<i>Don't leave your brother alone, okay?</i>

249
00:18:35,614 --> 00:18:38,408
[somber music playing]

250
00:18:38,492 --> 00:18:40,702
<i>Always take care of him.</i>

251
00:18:41,370 --> 00:18:43,413
<i>Always stand up for him, okay?</i>

252
00:18:45,499 --> 00:18:48,127
<i>Take care of him for life.</i>

253
00:18:49,336 --> 00:18:51,004
- [young Matmat grunting]
- [loud thud]

254
00:18:51,088 --> 00:18:53,507
[young Matmat] <i>Ow! </i>[crying]

255
00:18:53,590 --> 00:18:55,968
<i>Ow! It hurts!</i> [sobs]

256
