257
00:18:58,929 --> 00:19:01,140
<i>Patpat, it hurts!</i>

258
00:19:01,223 --> 00:19:03,016
[sobbing]

259
00:19:03,100 --> 00:19:05,894
<i>Look at you. You got hurt.</i>

260
00:19:05,978 --> 00:19:07,604
<i>Yes, Patpat.</i>

261
00:19:08,313 --> 00:19:12,151
<i>Patpat, you forgot your boxing gloves.</i>

262
00:19:13,193 --> 00:19:15,404
<i>These are for Patpat.</i>

263
00:19:15,487 --> 00:19:17,781
<i>This is for Matmat.</i>

264
00:19:18,323 --> 00:19:19,992
<i>Dino Boy!</i>

265
00:19:20,075 --> 00:19:22,703
[somber music continues]

266
00:19:22,786 --> 00:19:25,914
<i>This is mine, and those are yours, right?</i>

267
00:19:27,124 --> 00:19:30,711
[sobbing shakily] <i>M-Miss Mia or Matmat?</i>

268
00:19:30,794 --> 00:19:35,007
[somber music continues]

269
00:19:35,090 --> 00:19:37,176
[Patrick] <i>Of course, it's you, Matmat.</i>

270
00:19:37,259 --> 00:19:38,635
[Matmat] <i>Liar!</i>

271
00:19:38,719 --> 00:19:40,596
<i>You're a liar!</i> [sobs]

272
00:19:40,679 --> 00:19:44,725
<i>You told Mama you wanted me gone!</i>

273
00:19:44,808 --> 00:19:47,019
<i>"I hope Matmat just dies!"</i>

274
00:19:47,936 --> 00:19:52,191
<i>You told Mama you wanted me dead!</i>

275
00:19:52,941 --> 00:19:55,277
<i>You want me dead!</i>

276
00:19:55,611 --> 00:19:58,739
<i>I hope he just dies!</i>

277
00:19:58,822 --> 00:20:00,991
<i>I hope Matmat dies!</i>

278
00:20:02,784 --> 00:20:04,119
<i>P-Patpat!</i>

279
00:20:04,203 --> 00:20:07,789
[water rushing]

280
00:20:08,707 --> 00:20:11,168
[young Matmat grunts] <i>Patpat!</i>

281
00:20:14,588 --> 00:20:16,048
<i>Patpat!</i>

282
00:20:16,131 --> 00:20:18,759
- [water splashing]
- [breathes heavily, gurgles]

283
00:20:18,842 --> 00:20:19,968
<i>Pat--</i>

284
00:20:21,553 --> 00:20:22,721
<i>Patpat!</i>

285
00:20:22,804 --> 00:20:27,184
[somber music continues]

286
00:20:27,267 --> 00:20:28,310
[gasps]

287
00:20:28,393 --> 00:20:29,770
<i>Patpat--</i>

288
00:20:30,354 --> 00:20:31,521
<i>Matmat!</i>

289
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:34,650
<i>Matmat!</i>

290
00:20:36,401 --> 00:20:38,403
[young Matmat gurgles, breathes heavily]

291
00:20:39,947 --> 00:20:41,949
<i>- Matmat.</i>
<i>- Patpat.</i>

292
00:20:43,116 --> 00:20:47,663
[somber music continues]

293
00:20:48,080 --> 00:20:49,414
<i>Matmat!</i>

294
00:20:50,123 --> 00:20:51,333
[young Matmat breathes shakily]

295
00:20:51,416 --> 00:20:53,585
<i>Mama is still alive.</i>

296
00:20:55,087 --> 00:20:56,046
[thunder rumbles]

297
00:20:56,129 --> 00:20:58,131
[young Patrick] <i>Mama is in heaven now.</i>

298
00:20:58,799 --> 00:21:01,635
[young Matmat]
<i>We can't be with Mama anymore.</i>

299
00:21:02,594 --> 00:21:04,554
<i>Just like Trexy…</i>

300
00:21:04,638 --> 00:21:09,601
<i>Trexy's mother left him.</i>

301
00:21:10,227 --> 00:21:14,022
<i>- But--</i>
<i>- Mama left Matmat.</i>

302
00:21:14,106 --> 00:21:15,857
<i>- I'm still here, Matmat.</i>
<i>- Mama left him.</i>

303
00:21:15,941 --> 00:21:17,818
<i>I'm still here for you.</i>

304
00:21:18,402 --> 00:21:19,695
<i>I'm not leaving you.</i>

305
00:21:19,778 --> 00:21:21,989
<i>I'll be with you everywhere you go.</i>

306
00:21:23,323 --> 00:21:25,325
<i>You and me, Patpat?</i>

307
00:21:26,118 --> 00:21:28,078
<i>Yes, Matmat.</i> [sniffles]

308
00:21:28,161 --> 00:21:30,789
<i>Matmat and Patpat, right?</i>

309
00:21:31,748 --> 00:21:33,917
<i>Only Matmat and Patpat?</i>

310
00:21:34,001 --> 00:21:39,298
[somber music continues]

311
00:21:41,049 --> 00:21:42,175
<i>Yes.</i>

312
00:21:44,094 --> 00:21:45,846
<i>Only Matmat and Patpat.</i>

313
00:21:45,929 --> 00:21:48,807
- [somber music continues]
- [birds chirping]

314
00:21:48,890 --> 00:21:51,268
[Tessie] <i>Don't leave</i>
<i>your brother alone, okay?</i>

315
00:21:54,521 --> 00:21:56,606
<i>Always take care of him.</i>

316
00:21:56,690 --> 00:21:59,735
[somber music continues]

317
00:22:00,277 --> 00:22:02,446
<i>Always stand up for him, okay?</i>

318
00:22:06,867 --> 00:22:10,120
- [thuds]
<i>- Take care of him for life.</i>

319
00:22:10,203 --> 00:22:16,960
- [smacking]
- [somber music continues]

320
00:22:19,087 --> 00:22:20,505
[young Patrick] <i>Happy day.</i>

321
00:22:21,590 --> 00:22:23,550
[young Matmat] <i>Happy day.</i>

322
00:22:23,633 --> 00:22:28,346
[somber music continues]

323
00:22:30,849 --> 00:22:37,647
[music becomes tender]

324
00:22:49,117 --> 00:22:54,748
[tender music continues]

325
00:23:01,713 --> 00:23:03,215
[Mia] <i>You can't resist me.</i>

326
00:23:03,298 --> 00:23:05,425
<i>We have to end up together.</i>

327
00:23:07,010 --> 00:23:09,096
<i>Mama Dinosaur is so kind.</i>

328
00:23:09,179 --> 00:23:11,264
<i>But Bunso is not.</i>

329
00:23:11,348 --> 00:23:13,517
<i>Whatever you two went through</i>

330
00:23:13,600 --> 00:23:15,727
<i>is just part of who you are today.</i>

331
00:23:15,811 --> 00:23:17,896
[Gemma] <i>Think about your</i>
<i>own happiness too.</i>

332
00:23:17,979 --> 00:23:19,856
<i>That's not being selfish.</i>

333
00:23:21,316 --> 00:23:23,568
<i>- Where's Mia?</i>
<i>- She's at her house.</i>

334
00:23:23,652 --> 00:23:24,903
[object thuds]

335
00:23:25,695 --> 00:23:29,699
[tense music playing]
